</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_563" id="280v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Wolfharten von Eger, silberprenner zu Leipczk </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewnts<ex>chaft</ex></expan> bevor. <expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
                        Wolfhart, als du uns <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex>hast</expan> von des handels
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>zwisch<ex>en</ex></expan> dein und Eckhart
                            <expan>Neydu<ex>n</ex>gs</expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>, etc., das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                        wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> Eckhart <expan>Neydu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> für uns besandt und
                            <expan>ernstl<ex>ich</ex></expan> mit im <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        geredt, so steet dein schrift und sein antwurt gar ungleich. Wie
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> wilt du hie
                            <expan>zwisch<ex>en</ex></expan>
<app><note><q type="date"><expan>mittvast<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>schieristkunft<ex>ig</ex></expan></q>14.03.1423</note></app>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu uns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>, so solt
                        du <expan>dies<ex>elb</ex></expan> zeit zu und von uns für uns und die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>
                        und bey uns für <expan>all<ex>er</ex>menikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> geleyt
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>; alsdenn wil dir
                                <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> Eckhart Neydung
                            <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> slewnigs
                            <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> sein vor des reichs
                            <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns zu
                            <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
<expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich</expan>, des auch wir dir
                            <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>, ob du <expan>dein<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>scheinbott<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>deine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gwalt <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu uns
                                <expan>schike<ex>n</ex></expan> wöltst,
                            <expan>furderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> helffen
                            <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> on <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>.
                        Warczu du denn recht <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> solt und mit recht bey
                        uns erlangst, des <expan>gönne<ex>n</ex></expan> wir dir
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> teils wol.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.<lb/>Von
                        dem rate zu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
